<paragraph id="C882163289F589FCDEAE61B4A3B5A42B" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Graues Kreuzkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="B98BCF5F9D1F8388BF07B51302DE835F" pageId="null" pageNumber="499" type="description">
<paragraph id="99C26A8D4256A552C9C439752E078316" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<emphasis id="18C68B1A1F1D8833C04DE3BEF3623DBB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<normalizedToken id="775539A1BC349ED231BB904B80833224" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
dicht 
<normalizedToken id="783FD0FBE69A8681B4235DF073C837F1" originalValue="weißfilzig" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">weissfilzig</normalizedToken>
behaart, bis nahe an den Mittelnerv fiederteilig, 
<normalizedToken id="182F39B8A51A9ADD71B213FEDEA6E4E6" originalValue="plötzlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">ploetzlich</normalizedToken>
in den Stiel 
<normalizedToken id="CA1F8CCACB553A9A7C2E541D976486C6" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
, die Abschnitte oft nochmals stumpf 
<normalizedToken id="09BEE8289893C84960A9EEEFB23C7587" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
oder geteilt. 
<emphasis id="5011FAA09DC455E7246FD0C55AD269FD" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<normalizedToken id="DA1B8E335B7D16822B71A1E39088352D" originalValue="Blütenköpfe" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Bluetenkoepfe</normalizedToken>
3
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="3C512297A5D8255787BE64227926AD06" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">15 je Stengel</emphasis>
, in einer doldenartigen Traube, 
<emphasis id="712E7BCEE17FEE25D8D90DDF16C1E326" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">im Durchmesser 1</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="EC27E2E39A57869F30E660832EF7C2E6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">2 cm.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="3DCAB943C986952E6D0BFF321ADB03D8" originalValue="Hülle" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Huelle</normalizedToken>
<emphasis id="00DEE9455DC7F5840D811841082EF66B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">3</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="1BB8B0C13E59279AE122CAA3EDB01070" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">4</emphasis>
mm lang und 3-5 mm dick. 
<emphasis id="DC2A3CED0DEABA24C785CE6115BD479E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
Innere 
<normalizedToken id="17B890C6684A4D9963E9CDC1AB73385D" originalValue="Hüllblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Huellblaetter</normalizedToken>
6
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="450139BB32D88149DA814AD22818CF7B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">10</emphasis>
, 2,5-3,5 mm lang, kurz und 
<normalizedToken id="76786876DCEB183C98DFE354D77CAD86" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">+/-</normalizedToken>
stumpf zugespitzt, 
<emphasis id="39EE1DE11AA3E7B7B9964357EB8EC2F2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
mit 0,5 mm langer, roter Spitze. 
<normalizedToken id="A37D3ED0B9E8ADB0CA5A1CF8C066B44D" originalValue="Zungenblüten" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Zungenblueten</normalizedToken>
3
</emphasis>
- 
<emphasis id="35D48AEDAE92C18B9B1B0A1103706E22" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">6</emphasis>
, 5-8 mm lang und 1-2 mm breit. 
<normalizedToken id="ED00A5C957E7ADF243F552D76984F04D" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
fast kahl oder im obern Teil zerstreut behaart. - 
<normalizedToken id="6C229B374EF52690BEFB32A98110C0E1" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="31BE8A4DC283790F4A1E5A8CF6A6A6E5" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<emphasis id="C1816CB482858CA244C61F26538E4585" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="E5BF4221625CBFE863E2F624D733F080" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">40:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Wallis (Favarger 1949), aus botanischem Garten (Palmblad 1965).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="85F44225865B7911E674A5618D829AED" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<emphasis id="131018A886380873EBEECC462D9B11A2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin, seltener subalpin. Lockere, humose, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="35679BB80B8292082CDF3E219D6FCAD4" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Weiden, Felsschutt. 
<emphasis id="3B6EDB92B8370E851DC0FA82301774BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Caricetum curvulae</emphasis>
Brockmann-Jerosch 1907.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C3BCE7FEAF0F18F8F2ED6ED6D6141568" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">
<emphasis id="3FE928680C1E2A23140C12C07FBFFDCF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Verbreitung. Westalpin-apenninische Pflanze:</emphasis>
Westalpen (Alpes Maritimes bis Gotthard), mittlerer Apennin (Mommio). - Im Gebiet: Zentral- und 
<normalizedToken id="3943AE50F9DA17094C735EFFE38C0B1D" originalValue="Südalpen" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Suedalpen</normalizedToken>
(westlich des Sankt Gotthard), ziemlich 
<normalizedToken id="B3797BFFD3B524536D5794D2B2F9B0A7" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">haeufig</normalizedToken>
; Nordalpen (
<normalizedToken id="A4AA5393F4C5C48F25C6CA2D0A420DCE" originalValue="Mürren" pageId="null" pageNumber="499">Muerren</normalizedToken>
, Kiental, Sanetsch), selten.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
